description: Beneath an elegantly arched fel ceiling, a gold and crimson wyvern tapestry hangs on one of the textured ivory silk walls.  A carved mahogany box and a gold-veined black marble counter sit in opposite corners while a sphere-topped black marble fountain rests on a parquet golden oak floor.
